01:28:59,250 --> 01:29:04,250
- Big brother Zoll I held
out as long as I could.

1055
01:29:08,306 --> 01:29:10,801
(gasping)

1056
01:29:10,801 --> 01:29:13,551
(dramatic music)

1057
01:29:27,500 --> 01:29:29,230
- Now listen to me.

1058
01:29:29,230 --> 01:29:32,600
The last Torkarga female has just died.

1059
01:29:32,600 --> 01:29:36,213
Now there is no one left
to bear Torkarga children.

1060
01:29:38,000 --> 01:29:43,000
The Torkarga race is now
doomed to extinction.

1061
01:29:43,070 --> 01:29:47,290
Never forget that Harlock and the others

1062
01:29:47,290 --> 01:29:51,303
risked their lives to try
and give Torkarga a future.

1063
01:29:56,130 --> 01:29:59,213
- Thrust minus 80%, descent speed plus 10.

1064
01:30:00,520 --> 01:30:02,093
We're descending too fast.

1065
01:30:02,960 --> 01:30:06,326
- Tochiro maximum thrust, all engines.

1066
01:30:06,326 --> 01:30:09,243
(flames crackling)

1067
01:30:18,589 --> 01:30:20,021
- Come on.

1068
01:30:20,021 --> 01:30:22,938
(echoing laughing)

1069
01:30:33,630 --> 01:30:35,753
Hey we've started gaining thrust.

1070
01:31:14,428 --> 01:31:15,290
(laughing)

1071
01:31:15,290 --> 01:31:16,410
Harlock we did it.

1072
01:31:16,410 --> 01:31:18,893
We beat the Owen Stanley Witch of Space.

1073
01:31:20,837 --> 01:31:23,754
(flames crackling)

1074
01:31:33,050 --> 01:31:33,883
Oh, Mira.

1075
01:31:36,260 --> 01:31:38,283
- [La Mime] It's not only Mira who died.

1076
01:31:39,410 --> 01:31:40,729
- What?

1077
01:31:40,729 --> 01:31:45,729
(footsteps rapidly thudding)
(dramatic music)

1078
01:32:13,335 --> 01:32:15,502
(gasping)

1079
01:32:16,400 --> 01:32:18,800
- [La Mime] To cancel
out the life reaction

1080
01:32:18,800 --> 01:32:21,020
which was pulling the ship down.

1081
01:32:21,020 --> 01:32:25,443
- Everyone of them jumped
out into the river of flames?

1082
01:32:26,382 --> 01:32:31,382
(flames crackling)
(dramatic music)

1083
01:32:56,337 --> 01:32:59,254
(orchestral music)

1084
01:33:13,030 --> 01:33:15,070
- What, Harlock is coming back?

1085
01:33:15,070 --> 01:33:16,270
Never.

1086
01:33:16,270 --> 01:33:17,320
I'll alert the fleet.

1087
01:33:18,192 --> 01:33:19,313
Intercept that ship.

1088
01:33:22,104 --> 01:33:23,230
- [Zeda] Hold it.

1089
01:33:23,230 --> 01:33:25,730
Let him return safely to Earth.

1090
01:33:25,730 --> 01:33:27,170
- But why?

1091
01:33:27,170 --> 01:33:29,520
It's only one ship, let's shoot it down.

1092
01:33:29,520 --> 01:33:31,090
- Yes it's only one ship,

1093
01:33:31,090 --> 01:33:32,330
but are we going to mobilize

1094
01:33:32,330 --> 01:33:34,363
our entire fleet to shoot it down?

1095
01:33:35,340 --> 01:33:37,540
It will only make the
Earthmen revolt again.

1096
01:33:38,465 --> 01:33:40,715
(groaning)

1097
01:33:47,700 --> 01:33:50,650
- [Murigson] Commander
we must intercept it.

1098
01:33:50,650 --> 01:33:53,930
- They have formally
requested permission to land.

1099
01:33:53,930 --> 01:33:56,100
To send out our force to
shoot down a spaceship

1100
01:33:56,100 --> 01:33:58,680
with people who voluntarily
wish to return to this planet

1101
01:33:58,680 --> 01:34:03,010
where only misery awaits them
is something I cannot do.

1102
01:34:03,010 --> 01:34:03,937
They are very brave people

1103
01:34:03,937 --> 01:34:06,237
and it's time we showed
them a little respect.

1104
01:34:09,080 --> 01:34:12,594
- Maya Harlock is coming
back to the Earth.

1105
01:34:12,594 --> 01:34:14,140
(gasping)

1106
01:34:14,140 --> 01:34:17,020
He even made a formal
request to Commander Zeda

1107
01:34:17,020 --> 01:34:18,710
for permission to land here.

1108
01:34:18,710 --> 01:34:23,430
- He's coming back to Earth
and he'll only suffer again.

1109
01:34:23,430 --> 01:34:24,990
- I knew he would come back.

1110
01:34:24,990 --> 01:34:26,683
That's the kind of man he is.

1111
01:34:27,840 --> 01:34:29,460
The next time when his spaceship

1112
01:34:29,460 --> 01:34:31,763
leaves Earth let's go with him.

1113
01:34:33,480 --> 01:34:36,133
You've already done more
than enough here on Earth.

1114
01:34:53,680 --> 01:34:57,630
- [Maya On Radio] This is
the voice of Free Arcadia

1115
01:34:57,630 --> 01:35:02,490
broadcasting on a new frequency,
variable microwave 8390.

1116
01:35:04,400 --> 01:35:06,640
8390.

1117
01:35:06,640 --> 01:35:10,170
This is the voice of Free Arcadia

1118
01:35:10,170 --> 01:35:12,770
holding flowers in our hands.

1119
01:35:12,770 --> 01:35:16,620
Let's proceed to the desert
and welcome home our hope

1120
01:35:16,620 --> 01:35:18,510
for the future with flowers.

1121
01:35:22,011 --> 01:35:24,761
(dramatic music)

1122
01:35:26,958 --> 01:35:28,375
- [La Mime] Zoll.

1123
01:35:49,130 --> 01:35:51,940
- Zoll, I came back as I promised I would,

1124
01:35:52,847 --> 01:35:54,903
but I came back too late, forgive me.

1125
01:35:56,340 --> 01:35:57,693
I brought your sister Mira back with us.

1126
01:35:57,693 --> 01:36:01,505
- Come back to Torkarga, please save us.

1127
01:36:01,505 --> 01:36:05,755
Brother Zoll come back to
Torkarga, please save us.

1128
01:36:08,670 --> 01:36:10,600
- [Triter] You came all the way back here

1129
01:36:10,600 --> 01:36:13,500
just to say that to a dead man

1130
01:36:13,500 --> 01:36:16,640
even though you knew
we'd be waiting for you?

1131
01:36:16,640 --> 01:36:19,260
You're nothing but a stupid fool.

1132
01:36:19,260 --> 01:36:22,880
- If you don't understand
I feel sorry for you.

1133
01:36:22,880 --> 01:36:25,310
- Maybe what you've
done made you feel good,

1134
01:36:25,310 --> 01:36:28,260
but it puts Earth in a
very difficult position.

1135
01:36:28,260 --> 01:36:30,140
At present Earth has an agreement

1136
01:36:30,140 --> 01:36:32,980
to maintain cooperative
relations with Illumidus

1137
01:36:32,980 --> 01:36:35,370
even though some idiots
are planning a revolt

1138
01:36:35,370 --> 01:36:36,963
they will soon be suppressed.

1139
01:36:38,890 --> 01:36:40,787
We want to maintain peace on Earth

1140
01:36:40,787 --> 01:36:42,730
and a dangerous element like you

1141
01:36:42,730 --> 01:36:44,860
does not fit in with our present policy

1142
01:36:45,770 --> 01:36:47,590
and therefore our government orders you

1143
01:36:47,590 --> 01:36:49,763
to be permanently exiled from Earth.

1144
01:36:50,900 --> 01:36:52,290
- What's that?

1145
01:36:52,290 --> 01:36:54,650
- If you insist on remaining here on Earth

1146
01:36:54,650 --> 01:36:55,900
we will have no other course,

1147
01:36:55,900 --> 01:36:58,250
but to order our forces to fight you.

1148
01:36:58,250 --> 01:37:01,290
- You want to fight against us?

1149
01:37:01,290 --> 01:37:03,170
- You happen to be enemies of Earth.

1150
01:37:03,170 --> 01:37:04,383
- Enemies of Earth?

1151
01:37:13,590 --> 01:37:15,480
Alright, if you say we're not

1152
01:37:15,480 --> 01:37:18,050
welcome here than we shall leave.

1153
01:37:18,050 --> 01:37:19,020
- But Harlock.

1154
01:37:20,130 --> 01:37:21,200
- Harlock is right.

1155
01:37:21,200 --> 01:37:23,010
There's no need for anyone to stay here

1156
01:37:23,010 --> 01:37:25,520
and lower himself to the
level of being a pig.

1157
01:37:25,520 --> 01:37:26,520
- Emeraldas.

1158
01:37:28,085 --> 01:37:29,599
Emeraldas.

1159
01:37:29,599 --> 01:37:32,349
(dramatic music)

1160
01:37:34,950 --> 01:37:37,210
- The two of you there
listen very carefully,

1161
01:37:37,210 --> 01:37:39,600
the savageness of Murigson
who shot Maya and me

1162
01:37:39,600 --> 01:37:40,963
will long be remembered.

1163
01:37:43,290 --> 01:37:45,130
And the coward traitor who shot Zoll

1164
01:37:45,130 --> 01:37:47,000
will never be forgiven.

1165
01:37:47,000 --> 01:37:48,220
The ruthlessness of you two

1166
01:37:48,220 --> 01:37:51,820
who think nothing of the
life of man shall be avenged.

1167
01:37:51,820 --> 01:37:52,653
- But I was--

1168
01:37:52,653 --> 01:37:54,373
- Don't bother making excuses.

1169
01:37:55,339 --> 01:37:57,963
You can never justify what you have done.

1170
01:37:58,970 --> 01:38:03,000
- This is the voice of Free Arcadia.

1171
01:38:03,000 --> 01:38:05,120
This is Maya.

1172
01:38:05,120 --> 01:38:09,140
My dear Earthmen I wish to continue

1173
01:38:09,140 --> 01:38:11,673
to stay on the air and be with you.

1174
01:38:12,677 --> 01:38:16,857
Oh, I wanted to continue being with you.

1175
01:38:17,900 --> 01:38:21,230
But now I cannot keep going on.

1176
01:38:21,230 --> 01:38:22,433
Please forgive me.

1177
01:38:23,780 --> 01:38:27,823
This is the last voice of Free Arcadia.

1178
01:38:27,823 --> 01:38:28,656
- Maya.

1179
01:38:29,747 --> 01:38:31,903
- This is--
- Maya, that's enough.

1180
01:38:33,168 --> 01:38:34,660
It's alright.

1181
01:38:34,660 --> 01:38:37,403
- Harlock I had faith in you.

1182
01:38:38,820 --> 01:38:42,130
I knew in my heart that
you would come back again.

1183
01:38:42,130 --> 01:38:44,570
I knew that you would keep your promise

1184
01:38:44,570 --> 01:38:47,453
even though your friend
Zoll is no longer with us.

1185
01:38:49,350 --> 01:38:53,270
- We'll go together to the Sea of Stars.

1186
01:38:53,270 --> 01:38:58,270
- I've been dreaming all these
years of a beautiful place.

1187
01:38:59,270 --> 01:39:04,260
We used to play together
and now I will saail

1188
01:39:04,260 --> 01:39:09,260
in the Arcadia with you
over the Sea of Stars.

1189
01:39:14,451 --> 01:39:15,284
- Maya.

1190
01:39:17,736 --> 01:39:19,080
- Maya.

1191
01:39:19,080 --> 01:39:20,650
Maya.

1192
01:39:20,650 --> 01:39:22,320
Why did you leave me?

1193
01:39:22,320 --> 01:39:24,400
I had so many things to say.

1194
01:39:24,400 --> 01:39:26,010
Maya.

1195
01:39:26,010 --> 01:39:28,760
(dramatic music)

1196
01:39:33,890 --> 01:39:37,150
- Everyone, Maya who kept
appealing to all of you

1197
01:39:37,150 --> 01:39:40,770
to believe in a better
future for Earth is now gone

1198
01:39:40,770 --> 01:39:42,290
and the government of Earth has just

1199
01:39:42,290 --> 01:39:45,290
condemned all of us to permanent exile.

1200
01:39:45,290 --> 01:39:47,980
All of you beware, for
the Earth will become

1201
01:39:47,980 --> 01:39:51,593
a second Torkarga and how
will you survive that?

1202
01:39:52,970 --> 01:39:54,110
I urge all of you all of you

1203
01:39:54,110 --> 01:39:56,743
to remember the voice of Free Arcadia.

1204
01:39:58,470 --> 01:39:59,980
- That's enough Tochiro.

1205
01:39:59,980 --> 01:40:02,180
Since we've been exiled
we better leave now.

1206
01:40:12,560 --> 01:40:14,610
Under that flag is there anyone

1207
01:40:14,610 --> 01:40:16,533
among you who wants to join us?

1208
01:40:17,517 --> 01:40:20,267
(dramatic music)

1209
01:40:35,510 --> 01:40:38,070
Under that flag, do you pledge to fight

1210
01:40:38,070 --> 01:40:39,500
for those who believe in freedom?

1211
01:40:39,500 --> 01:40:40,333
- I do.

1212
01:40:40,333 --> 01:40:41,770
- You can never return.

1213
01:40:41,770 --> 01:40:44,453
- The Sea of Stars will be
our home, our only home.

1214
01:40:57,977 --> 01:41:00,477
(tense music)

1215
01:41:06,970 --> 01:41:07,803
- Let's go.

1216
01:41:16,070 --> 01:41:18,360
- Keep your filthy hands off.

1217
01:41:18,360 --> 01:41:20,400
He was my best friend.

1218
01:41:20,400 --> 01:41:21,300
- Hold it Harlock.

1219
01:41:23,860 --> 01:41:26,370
I am also a proud man and if you wish

1220
01:41:26,370 --> 01:41:29,420
to depart safely you
must first go through me.

1221
01:41:29,420 --> 01:41:31,690
- A duel?
- Yes.

1222
01:41:31,690 --> 01:41:34,390
And the choice of weapons
and the place shall be mine.

1223
01:41:36,770 --> 01:41:39,080
By custom a duel is fought one to one

1224
01:41:39,080 --> 01:41:40,420
and I forbid interference.

1225
01:41:40,420 --> 01:41:41,343
- Very well.

1226
01:41:44,560 --> 01:41:47,313
- Commander you can't let
that man get away now.

1227
01:41:49,098 --> 01:41:50,574
(grunting)

1228
01:41:50,574 --> 01:41:53,574
(suspenseful music)

1229
01:41:56,910 --> 01:41:58,280
- You object to my decision

1230
01:41:58,280 --> 01:42:00,477
and you raise a weapon in defiance of me

1231
01:42:00,477 --> 01:42:02,363
and let that be the end of you.

1232
01:42:03,953 --> 01:42:06,370
(gun firing)

1233
01:42:30,472 --> 01:42:32,910
- [Maya] Now my loved one sets out

1234
01:42:32,910 --> 01:42:36,320
with the flag of our freedom.

1235
01:42:36,320 --> 01:42:39,653
Farewell until the day
you come back to me.

1236
01:42:40,540 --> 01:42:41,843
I believe in you.

1237
01:42:42,880 --> 01:42:45,230
No matter how far apart we may be

1238
01:42:46,070 --> 01:42:48,587
I know that you will
never forget the Earth.

1239
01:42:49,867 --> 01:42:52,617
(dramatic music)

1240
01:43:11,420 --> 01:43:14,360
No one can keep you from leaving

1241
01:43:14,360 --> 01:43:17,116
with your flag floating high.

1242
01:43:17,116 --> 01:43:19,410
Farewell my Harlock.

1243
01:43:19,410 --> 01:43:22,520
You always had faith and hope in tomorrow

1244
01:43:22,520 --> 01:43:24,453
no matter what the circumstances.

1245
01:43:25,405 --> 01:43:29,900
And I am proud to have shared
my days in the past with you.

1246
01:43:29,900 --> 01:43:33,313
I pray that your future will
be the one you believe in.

1247
01:43:34,480 --> 01:43:36,840
Farewell my dear Harlock.

1248
01:43:36,840 --> 01:43:38,500
Live on with hope.

1249
01:43:38,500 --> 01:43:39,433
Live forever.

1250
01:43:41,068 --> 01:43:44,180
I see it so clearly deep inside

1251
01:43:44,180 --> 01:43:48,893
your heart the flame is burning,
believing in your future.

1252
01:43:49,780 --> 01:43:53,804
The fire of the man who will
never betray his friends.

1253
01:43:53,804 --> 01:43:57,793
I love you and I will be apart
of the flame in your heart.

1254
01:43:58,700 --> 01:44:03,487
Deep in you heart I will
be with you forever.

1255
01:44:03,487 --> 01:44:06,237
(dramatic music)

1256
01:44:25,403 --> 01:44:27,236
- [Emeraldas] Harlock.

1257
01:44:29,320 --> 01:44:31,720
Look at the red pirate flag on my ship.

1258
01:44:31,720 --> 01:44:34,210
It's the color of Maya's blood.

1259
01:44:34,210 --> 01:44:37,200
Maya's white dress dyed like her blood,

1260
01:44:37,200 --> 01:44:39,060
the flag of a pirate.

1261
01:44:39,060 --> 01:44:41,800
The red badge of freedom
that man is seeking.

1262
01:44:41,800 --> 01:44:43,493
The flag of my freedom.

1263
01:44:46,820 --> 01:44:49,780
- Maya was Harlock's--

1264
01:44:49,780 --> 01:44:51,530
- That's right the kind of woman

1265
01:44:51,530 --> 01:44:53,860
who never tired down the one she loved.

1266
01:44:53,860 --> 01:44:57,190
The kind of woman even you
would've fallen in love with.

1267
01:44:58,679 --> 01:45:01,429
(dramatic music)

1268
01:45:34,634 --> 01:45:35,467
- Ah?

1269
01:45:36,880 --> 01:45:38,623
It's signaling follow me.

1270
01:45:39,610 --> 01:45:41,253
That's the Illumidus flag ship.

1271
01:45:46,918 --> 01:45:50,820
- Harlock, I've found
a true Earthman in you

1272
01:45:50,820 --> 01:45:52,560
that no computer could fathom

1273
01:45:53,580 --> 01:45:58,580
and Tochiro came out
the same and also Maya.

1274
01:45:59,790 --> 01:46:02,700
Therefore not as commander
of the Earth Occupation Force

1275
01:46:02,700 --> 01:46:06,073
but as man to man I am determined
to have a duel with you.

1276
01:46:09,160 --> 01:46:11,617
And I hope you will
fight without restraint.

1277
01:46:18,062 --> 01:46:19,912
- [Woman] Contact report.

1278
01:46:19,912 --> 01:46:23,745
The Illumidus fleet
attack force of 624 ships.

1279
01:46:25,176 --> 01:46:27,343
(gasping)

1280
01:46:29,120 --> 01:46:30,590
- I think Commander Zeda

1281
01:46:30,590 --> 01:46:33,030
is trying to pull us away
in the opposite direction

1282
01:46:33,030 --> 01:46:35,480
from the area the Illumidus
fleet is approaching.

1283
01:46:49,770 --> 01:46:52,103
- Increase our thrust.
- Roger.

1284
01:46:53,720 --> 01:46:55,570
We're closing fast on the enemy ship.

1285
01:47:34,040 --> 01:47:36,420
- Take combat positions.

1286
01:47:36,420 --> 01:47:37,963
Combat speed five.

1287
01:47:39,540 --> 01:47:41,693
All turrets combat ready.

1288
01:48:31,503 --> 01:48:34,420
(orchestral music)

1289
01:48:39,630 --> 01:48:42,550
Open all reverse jets and accelerate.

1290
01:48:42,550 --> 01:48:45,113
- [Tochiro] Roger, reduce
to combat speed three.

1291
01:48:51,210 --> 01:48:54,223
- Port side gunner
aligned, stand by to fire.

1292
01:48:55,260 --> 01:48:58,180
Fire at 0.1 garm intervals.

1293
01:48:58,180 --> 01:49:00,123
30 micro-garms before volley.

1294
01:49:04,160 --> 01:49:06,710
- Relative velocity, 128,000.

1295
01:49:06,710 --> 01:49:09,743
Altitude variance zero.

1296
01:49:12,010 --> 01:49:14,620
Main gun tracking speed in sync.

1297
01:49:14,620 --> 01:49:16,563
10 seconds before discharge.

1298
01:49:19,680 --> 01:49:24,680
Eight, seven, six, five,
four, three, two, one.

1299
01:49:28,490 --> 01:49:29,795
- Fire.

1300
01:49:29,795 --> 01:49:30,959
- Fire.

1301
01:49:30,959 --> 01:49:33,459
(guns firing)

1302
01:49:37,819 --> 01:49:38,990
(yelling)

1303
01:49:38,990 --> 01:49:41,490
(guns firing)

1304
01:49:54,847 --> 01:49:57,930
(explosions booming)

1305
01:49:58,860 --> 01:50:01,027
(yelling)

1306
01:50:01,870 --> 01:50:05,359
- Port side aft dispatch
damage control team.

1307
01:50:05,359 --> 01:50:07,859
(guns firing)

1308
01:50:13,742 --> 01:50:15,180
- Give me a damage assessment report.

1309
01:50:15,180 --> 01:50:17,370
